{"tid":2125330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華為前研究員：港科研恐遭國際封殺","createTime":"2020-07-26T06:26:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T12:15:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"df4fe1f6a5177482c3a11e854d7e7c579797fd89","tid":2125330,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:26:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/Z45H2SN2ZBQPDHTEAPYNCLQ5FE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FZ45H2SN2ZBQPDHTEAPYNCLQ5FE%2F&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=07cfba1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200726%2FZ45H2SN2ZBQPDHTEAPYNCLQ5FE%2F&h=ef345f60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200726/Z45H2SN2ZBQPDHTEAPYNCLQ5FE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華為前研究員：港科研恐遭國際封殺<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美。。。。。。。<br />\n。。。。。。最先進的技術在美國，此行政命令肯定會窒礙香港研究。美國封殺華為後其他國家相繼跟隨，他擔心香港或步華為後塵，面臨類似困境。<br />\n<br />\n陳慶鴻1977年在中大考獲碩士學位後，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lJo94MnZn1Vuwjym88XA2cuvRHQ=/652x398/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LTMT7I4ARS2B2FAAMMGXB3VCMA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FlJo94MnZn1Vuwjym88XA2cuvRHQ%3D%2F652x398%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLTMT7I4ARS2B2FAAMMGXB3VCMA.gif&h=789c4115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳慶鴻指倘港人連通訊也遭監控，海外對香港將更無信心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指政府截取通訊形式如伊朗<br />\n<br />\n談到美國對港措施，陳多次形容是「兩敗俱傷」，因交流越多對兩地科研越有幫助，若失去自由往來和交流的環境，科研人員就被「綁實」。他不希望國家民族之間因政治原因無法合作。現時最先進人工智能技術在美國，主因是美國吸納世界各地人才，當中亦包括中國人，合作中斷對美國來說雖有損失，「但係損失無香港咁大，因為佢（美國）無咗中國，都仲有印度、日本、韓國，有其他人才可以吸納」。<br />\n<br />\n陳更擔心，其他。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他估計，美國憂慮香港取得技術後，或會帶到中國，於是將對中國的政策適用於香港。他憂慮，此後美國公司與香港公司交流將受限制，若技術不能交流，研究會「好難做」，或令投資者避免將研究的重點放在香港。<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法下，政府截取通訊權力增，陳直言「似乎就好似伊朗個形式咁樣」，情況令人擔心。他認為，通訊有如水電，是生活必需品，若政府用來對付人民，外國會從人道立場，寧不再向這些國家出售技術。他擔心，若港人的通訊如微訊般被監控，海外對香港將更無信心。"},{"pid":"a1aa08acede516a753dc2f576eacb7094b60e6e8","tid":2125330,"uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:27:11.000Z","msg":"我唔擔心wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327e5463008b288bd153c99c9b72ce862b2773ae","tid":2125330,"uid":310846,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"攬炒嘛！<br />\n19政府爭取返嚟<br />\n一國一制<br />\n香港市"},{"pid":"d756375954ac69d5f6bbbf205cc98bee007071f0","tid":2125330,"uid":42740,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:29:55.000Z","msg":"基本法腐乳怕閪"},{"pid":"5259000dedb3d2c36847dc11cc6160376a8fe89c","tid":2125330,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:31:53.000Z","msg":"恐國際又乜乜柒柒唔封殺香港科研 驚懲罰到香港人"},{"pid":"8603e6d5aebd250deffccfda53bfc1dc90afdca9","tid":2125330,"uid":10757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"香港都冇科研 得大陸佬有姐 咁叫香港科研<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7509fbf6d36ad91b41a0990ff58b3301c0061ed","tid":2125330,"uid":66099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:34:04.000Z","msg":"香港都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />daydaycook都可以話係it人"},{"pid":"2d9eb6cbc9d5288f987b1af962cb02967362eacd","tid":2125330,"uid":100772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:35:16.000Z","msg":"香港科研一直比香港政府封殺<br />\n一直都係比錢中國公司做"},{"pid":"9c2a0d6ca70cff3c33220f87a2e17367ae255d76","tid":2125330,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"華為前研究員 完"},{"pid":"931dda44ef